WEBVTT

00:03.539 --> 00:08.105
Talk show host Oprah Winfrey says she encountered racism while shopping in Switzerland,...

00:08.277 --> 00:10.465
...and the national tourism office agrees.

00:10.646 --> 00:14.629
The media mogul, who is one of the world's richest women, told Entertainment Tonight...

00:14.902 --> 00:18.167
...that a shop assistant in Zurich refused to show her a handbag...

00:18.246 --> 00:20.148
...because it was too expensive for her.

00:20.447 --> 00:23.922
A spokeswoman for the Swiss tourism office told the Associated Press,...

00:24.147 --> 00:26.281
..."We are very sorry for what happened to her."

00:26.465 --> 00:29.763
The tourism office also posted an apology on Twitter saying,...

00:29.994 --> 00:31.953
..."This person acted terribly wrong."

